      <h4>⚠️ Important Disclaimer</h4>
      <p>This analysis is for educational and informational purposes only. It is not investment advice, a recommendation to buy or sell securities, or a solicitation of any kind. All investments carry risk, including the loss of principal.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
